name: Kabuki Panda - KuD-060
description: Kabuki Panda was born as a performer. No doubt that he has skill in sing, dance and acting on stage. He is a humble panda with lots of talent, that make many love and idolize him. People from any level of society always make his theatre full of audiences. His love for his job and culture always make his show draw many attention. And he always want to teach newer generation of this cultural entertaiment that he love. He want to make sure that this tradition is passed down to newer generation and make this tradition to be always be respected even though era has changes.
